                    </li>
                    <li>Sneak/Trick Attack now stack with BLU spells.</li>
                    <li>Blue magic hit rate/accuracy reworked.</li>
                    <li>Job traits persist when zoning.</li>
                    <li>Occultation MP cost reduced to 50.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section id="geo" class="job-section">
