                <h3>Masteries</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>[1]</strong> Use 100 Indi spells and gain 2x Duration
                        and 2x Range for your Indi spells.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>[2]</strong> Use 100 Geo spells and gain 2x Range
