                <h2>Red Mage</h2>
                <h3>Masteries</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>[1]</strong> After casting 100 enfeebling spells your
                        enfeebling spells gain 10% spell accuracy while playing Red
                        Mage.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>[2]</strong> After casting 150 enhancing magic spells
                        gain 50% increased enhancing magic duration.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>[3]</strong> After casting Haste 100 times on a RNG
